        "file": "EV061_08"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥和树",
      "lines": [
        "「我也快要射了！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・愛液",
        "file": "EV061_08"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥凉菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "SUZU_003_SUZU006C_020",
        "file": "voice/suzu_003_suzu006C_020.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「哦呵呵！在小穴里，直接射进去！射得满满的！最深处一下子喷出来！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・愛液",
        "file": "EV061_08"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "",
        "姐姐用力夹紧颤抖的双腿，将丰满的屁股顶了过来。",
        "",
        "然后，深深吞咽到根部，疯狂地摇摆着腰部。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・愛液",
        "file": "EV061_08"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥凉菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "SUZU_003_SUZU006C_021",
        "file": "voice/suzu_003_suzu006C_021.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「想要用射精的肉棒来达到高潮！呼，呼！",
        "嗯哦，小穴，让我中出去！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・愛液",
        "file": "EV061_08"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "被汗水和爱液浸湿的柔软臀肉，轻轻晃动着，刺激着根部和睾丸。",
        "",
        "阴道肌肉紧紧地夹住物体，起伏不停，阴道深处紧贴着龟头。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・愛液",
        "file": "EV061_08"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥凉菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "SUZU_003_SUZU006C_022",
        "file": "voice/suzu_003_suzu006C_022.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「呼，呼！想要在里面，感受炽热！",
        "求求你了！在小穴的深处，请给我！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・愛液",
        "file": "EV061_08"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "凉姐仰起身子，阴道紧紧收缩。",
        "就像要挤出精液一样。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・愛液",
        "file": "EV061_08"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥凉菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "SUZU_003_SUZU006C_023",
        "file": "voice/suzu_003_suzu006C_023.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊咕！嗯呵呵，要射了，要射了～！",
        "太厉害了！太厉害的高潮来了！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・愛液",
        "file": "EV061_08"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "下一刻，我深入最深处，并射精了。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・愛液",
        "file": "EV061_08"
      },
      "se": [
        {
          "code": "8201B",
          "file": "se/8201b.ogg"
        }
      ],
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "噗哔哔哔！咚哔哔！滋滋滋！"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      },
      "flash": 3
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥凉菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "SUZU_003_SUZU006C_024",
        "file": "voice/suzu_003_suzu006C_024.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊咕！？啊，热热的，来了！",
        "呼哦，哦，要高潮了，嗯呼呼！！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "se": [
        {
          "code": "8351A",
          "file": "se/8351a.ogg"
        }
      ],
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "凉姐的身体颤抖着。",
        "她一边剧烈地高潮，一边用腰部顶着我，扭动着，刺激着龟头。",
        "",
        "因此，吸附在阴道深处的东西不停地扭动着，我的头脑变得一片空白。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      },
      "flash": 2
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥凉菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "SUZU_003_SUZU006C_025",
        "file": "voice/suzu_003_suzu006C_025.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯哦！啊哈，喷出来了，热热的！",
        "啊啊～！被精液填满感到幸福！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "se": [
        {
          "code": "8351A",
          "file": "se/8351a.ogg"
        }
      ],
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "像直接吸入精液一样的强烈快感。",
        "腰部颤抖着，精液源源不断地喷射出来。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "se": [
        {
          "code": "8201B",
          "file": "se/8201b.ogg"
        }
      ],
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      },
      "flash": 2
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥凉菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "SUZU_003_SUZU006C_026",
        "file": "voice/suzu_003_suzu006C_026.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「呼哦哦！这个，这个！小穴被精液塞满了，好，好幸福啊！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      },
      "flash": 3
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "",
        "凉姐被阴道充满精液而陶醉其中。",
        "我也沉浸在极度的快感中，忘记了自我，不停地抽送着。",
        "",
        "炽热而疼痛的龟头，紧紧地顶在深处。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "se": [
        {
          "code": "8201B",
          "file": "se/8201b.ogg"
        }
      ],
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥凉菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "SUZU_003_SUZU006C_027",
        "file": "voice/suzu_003_suzu006C_027.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「噢，噢哦！呼哦，好舒服，好爽！",
        "头，哈呀，感觉要变得奇怪了！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "se": [
        {
          "code": "8351A",
          "file": "se/8351a.ogg"
        }
      ],
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      },
      "flash": 3
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "凉姐也扭动着屁股接纳着我。",
        "感觉龟头被吸了进去。",
        "在这种状态下扭动腰部，感觉一直在外面。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      },
      "flash": 2
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥凉菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "SUZU_003_SUZU006C_028",
        "file": "voice/suzu_003_suzu006C_028.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「嗯呜哦！正在高潮中，还在继续……啊啊，这样下去，会坏掉的……！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "",
        "一次又一次，快感从身体中释放出去。",
        "我们一段时间内保持深度连接，不停地晃动身体。",
        "",
        "大量的精液从连接处溢出来。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥凉菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "SUZU_003_SUZU006C_029",
        "file": "voice/suzu_003_suzu006C_029.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「啊啊太厉害了……太厉害了……哈啊，小穴和子宫都好热！」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "",
        "高潮感慢慢退去，留下深深的余韵。",
        "被精液覆盖的阴道黏黏地缠绕着，感觉非常舒服。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・射精",
        "file": "EV061_09"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥凉菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "SUZU_003_SUZU006C_030",
        "file": "voice/suzu_003_suzu006C_030.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「哈啊，果然和弟弟做爱最棒了！",
        "深处射精的肉棒触感真是太棒了……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・精液たれ",
        "file": "EV061_12"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "冷静下来后，才发现全身都出了一身汗。",
        ""
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#EV061・アヘ顔・挿入・眉寄せ・精液たれ",
        "file": "EV061_12"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "narration",
      "lines": [
        "房间里弥漫着汗水，爱液和精液的气味。"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#背景・黒一色",
        "file": "BG_BLACK"
      },
      "bgv": {
        "id": "BGV_SUZU_H003A",
        "file": "voice/BGV_suzu_h003a.ogg"
      }
    },
    {
      "kind": "line",
      "who": "古桥绫菜",
      "voice": {
        "id": "AYAN_003_SUZU006B_002",
        "file": "voice/ayan_003_suzu006B_002.ogg"
      },
      "lines": [
        "「凉酱，差不多该……」"
      ],
      "bg": {
        "label": "#背景・古橋家リビング（昼）",
